Poland’s Komorowski Says Euro Crisis Is Turning Point for EU

-- B y   D a v i d   M c Q u a i d
-- 
2011-10-21T07:44:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/poland-s-komorowski-says-euro-crisis-is-turning-point-for-eu.html
The European Union’s debt crisis is
a turning point in the bloc’s history that shows member states
must impose more fiscal discipline, Polish President Bronislaw
Komorowski said today in a speech at a central banking
conference in Warsaw.  Poland intends to fulfill the requirements for membership
in the euro area, Komorowski said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David McQuaid at 
 dmcquaid1@bloomberg.net  